OL,3,CCoroner warns of dangers at home after
OL,4,Cchild's death
OL,6,FA coroner has said that a Cookstown
OL,7,Ffamily hopes "a public safety message
OL,8,Fwill get out there" after their 15-
OL,9,Fmonth-old daughter died in her cot
OL,10,Fafter reaching her brother's gym bag
OL,11,Fcord.
OL,13,FBelfast Coroner's Court heard how
OL,14,Fstrangulation can render a child
OL,15,Funconscious in under 10 seconds, and
OL,16,Fthat death can follow in a matter of
OL,17,Fminutes.
OL,19,FEmily Whinnery was 15 months old when
OL,20,Fshe died after pulling her brother's
OL,21,Fgym bag cord into her cot.
OL,26,@pD@SO]
