OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1778270754
OL,3,CCoroner warns of dangers at home after
OL,4,Cchild's death
OL,6,FBelfast Coroner's Court heard how the
OL,7,FCookstown toddler shared a room with
OL,8,Fher five-year-old brother.
OL,10,FHe didn't stay in his room that night
OL,11,F- but his black gym bag was hung from
OL,12,Fthe post of his bunk-bed.
OL,14,FPolice statements read in court noted
OL,15,Fhow the cord of the bag was long
OL,16,Fenough to reach the floor and that it
OL,17,Fcould be reached from the cot.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
