FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1778270754
OL,3,CCoroner warns of dangers at home after
OL,4,Cchild's death
OL,6,FA statement from Emily's mother,
OL,7,FStacey Whinnery, read that Emily was a
OL,8,Fgood sleeper and was cutting teeth and
OL,9,Fhad conjunctivitis at the time - and
OL,10,Fthat she let Emily sleep on until 11am.
OL,12,FShe said when she went into Emily's
OL,13,Froom, her lips and mouth were blue,
OL,14,Fher body felt limp and a cord of her
OL,15,Fbrother's gym bag was around her neck.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
