OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1778270754
OL,3,CCoroner warns of dangers at home after
OL,4,Cchild's death
OL,6,FIn the transcript of the 999 call read
OL,7,Fout in court, Emily's mother said to
OL,8,Fthe police handler "oh my god she's
OL,9,Fdead, oh my god she's dead.... She's
OL,10,Fgot a drawstring cord around her neck,
OL,11,FI think she's choked... she's not
OL,12,Fbreathing, oh my god" before she began
OL,13,Fcarrying out CPR while awaiting for
OL,14,Fthe ambulance crew to arrive.
OL,16,FThey attempted to resuscitate Emily
OL,17,Fbefore agreeing that she was dead.
OL,19,FA pathologist confirmed the cause of
OL,20,Fdeath was ligature compression of the
OL,21,Fneck.
OL,26,@pD@TOUtD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
